  "title": "Barista - Up to $3.5k/month",
  "description": "<p><strong>Monthly Salary: Up to $3,500 (Negotiable)</strong><br /><strong>Working Address: Tanjong Pagar</strong><br /><br /><strong>Working hours: 5 Days, 44 hours</strong><br /><br /><br /><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Offer high levels of customer service to all customers consistently.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and serve pies and drinks accurately per the SOP and in a timely manner.</p></li><li><p>Clean and maintain brewing equipment as needed.</p></li><li><p>Monitor the condition of brewing equipment and report any maintenance issues.</p></li><li><p>Have full knowledge of the menu to share recommendations with customers.</p></li><li><p>Perform quality checks on pies and drinks, keeping spoilage to a minimum.</p></li><li><p>Maintain an adequate supply of all stocks in inventory, ensuring proper storage and<br />refrigeration for daily operations.</p></li><li><p>Uphold strict hygiene standards of the studio and all equipment.</p></li><li><p>Fulfil opening and closing duties.</p></li><li><p>Ad-hoc duties as assigned by Management.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>WSQ food hygiene certification</p></li><li><p>Warm and cheerful personality</p></li><li><p>Adaptable and self-motivated in completing assigned tasks</p></li><li><p>Detail-oriented</p></li><li><p>Values teamwork<br /></p><p></p></li></ul><p>Nextbeat Singapore Pte. Ltd.</p><p>EA License Number: 22C1267</p><p>EA Personnel No: R22107133</p>",
